sentence: Looking at options trading activity among components of the S&P 500 index, there is noteworthy activity today in Salesforce.com Inc (Symbol: CRM), where a total volume of 51,202 contracts has been traded thus far today, a contract volume which is representative of approximately 5.1 million underlying shares (given that every 1 contract represents 100 underlying shares).
That number works out to 108.4% of CRM's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 4.7 million shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $155 strike call option expiring September 20, 2019, with 9,685 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 968,500 underlying shares of CRM.
